data.description: Back on the market! Beautiful home in Adelanto in a very nice and quiet neighborhood. This spacious 2-story, 6 bedroom, 3 bathroom home has a 3 cars garage as well as RV parking with electric and water hook-ups. Large master bedroom has a walk-in closet with an ensuite that features a garden tub and shower. More features include high vaulted ceilings, ceiling fans and custom wood blinds, open floor plan with a kitchen and breakfast nook, fireplace in living room, formal dining area, indoor laundry, cute front porch, large backyard with a covered patio, sprinkler system in the front and back yard. There is also a large wooden shed that could be used for storage, hobby room, workshop, or etc. Very close to shopping, freeways, and has beautiful mountain views. This home is definitely a MUST SEE!!!
